## 3 — API (`modules/uba/api/router.py`) ← **[REWRITE]**

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|--------|----------|------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/status` | operator+ | Module + stats |
| `GET` | `/config` | operator+ | Read UBA settings |
| `PUT` | `/config` | admin | Update thresholds |
| `GET` | `/users` | operator+ | List all user profiles |
| `GET` | `/users/{username}` | operator+ | Detail for one user |
| `DELETE` | `/users/{username}/reset` | admin | Clear user's baseline |
| `GET` | `/users/{username}/events` | operator+ | Events for a user |
| `GET` | `/events` | operator+ | All events, filterable by severity/date |
| `GET` | `/alerts` | operator+ | Events with risk >= high |
| `POST` | `/events` | admin | Manually submit an event for analysis |

